Experience Serenity
by the River
Nestled along the picturesque Haines Creek River, our campground boasts 600 feet of dock space, making it a haven for fishing enthusiasts and nature lovers alike. Each site offers full hookups with options for both 30 and 50 amp electric connections, complete with convenient cement pads for added comfort.
Stay connected with complimentary Wi-Fi available at two designated hotspots within the park, with many sites equipped for direct access. Shaded by majestic old oak and palm trees, our park provides a serene escape, while paved streets and streetlights ensure easy navigation and safety.
Whether you're seeking a vibrant winter getaway filled with activities, parties, and dinners, or looking for a permanent home in our welcoming community, our campground is your ideal destination all year round.
